        <p style="color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 1em 0;">
         Series D investors bought it, as did investors in the company\xe2\x80\x99s $433 million May 2015 Series E and its $690 million November 2016 Series F. But no one bought Neumann\xe2\x80\x99s vision to be more than just office space than his Series G lead: Softbank\xe2\x80\x99s Masa Son.
        </p>
        <p style="color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 1em 0;">
         When Adam met Masa in
         <a href="https://email.mg2.substack.com/c/eJxFkcuurCAQRb-mmWF4qwMGZ3J_wxRStqQVDOA1_v2huwcnIVRSj-ydtWeo-Ez5tkcqlby_qd4H2ohX2bBWzOQsmKfgLTdikFqNxFvl-aAHEsq0ZMQdwmZrPpEcp9vCDDWk-LlgTGiy2oVJ9LNRvJ8NB9b3zjmhei64Qw5u-OrC6QPGGS3-x3yniGSza61Hecifh_jX3nVd3QKlzmk_IN5dq607MiWMUua9gEvzQtd00boi9Snt6OkOBWhJkYKHnUY8d4iRZtw-RssaDlqw0guvlF-07b1vcwJPa6I-lKbYMAQrmOBMipEL3fO-452SwiyL62F24zJolEZ5jWox47x4LcVDsf0punK6UmF-vf2SbGOqLuUQn238WmHH7TNo7KZW9zOGek8YwW3ov1jrN50P6OmJEXNLzU9QWya8Z0IYLZQWX4yNu1RyGJQeSVP2qV3FP9FfOYypWA" style="color: #1a1a1a; text-decoration: underline;">
          December 2016
         </a>
         , the SoftBank CEO showed up two hours late, told Neumann he had 12 minutes for a tour, and suggested they continue the conversation in the car. There, after knowing each other for 28 minutes, Son famously whipped out an iPad, drew up terms for a $4.4 billion investment, and asked Neumann to sign. He did.
        </p>
        <p style="color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 1em 0;">
         Masa, according to Neumann, appreciated that he was crazy, but
         <strong>
          thought that he needed to get
         </strong>
         <em>
          <strong>
           crazier
          </strong>
         </em>
         <strong>
          .
         </strong>
         Oh, he did.
        </p>
        <p style="color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 1em 0;">
         In the two and a half years between closing that investment and filing to go public, in addition to accelerating the expansion of its core business, WeWork:
        </p>
        <ul style="margin: 1em 0;">
         <li style="margin: 3.75px 0 3.75px 7.5px; mso-special-format: bullet;">
          <p style="color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0;">
           Invested in a wave pool company,
           <a href="https://email.mg2.substack.com/c/eJxFkcGu4yAMRb-m7IiCgUAWLN5mfiMiYFqmCURAXtS_H9ouRrJsWVdX1zp2tuE9l5c5cm3k3Zb2OtAkvOqGrWEhZ8WyRG_YBJpLMRNvhGdaahLrEgribuNmWjmRHOe6RWdbzOnjGEeQ5GEkA6GF08AgCKUgKO95CBNXs-UyTN9ce_qIyaHBXyyvnJBs5tHaUW_85wZ_el3XNVz17-Dy3jdbWnQb1reAVy5P2uwTK7XUx4PGRNsD6WV_kR45b3Q9a0xYK2WSjWqSSo8kGhiBjRxmBlIxNbBBcJhCWJV16xy0RD4JL1GEaXbBSw43Me53GOq51mbd830LKSbltuYS073Lz4fdcfsIncfS536m2F4LJrtu6L-o2pf4B95yx4Slf8IvtnXOTI0AkwQh4Yums-SCay3kTHqyz92V_of-A7Cql2w" style="color: #1a1a1a; text-decoration: underline;">
            WaveGarden
           </a>
          </p>
         </li>
         <li style="margin: 3.75px 0 3.75px 7.5px; mso-special-format: bullet;">
          <p style="color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0;">
           Opened its first gym/spa,
           <a href="https://email.mg2.substack.com/c/eJxFkE1uxCAMhU8z7BoFA_lZsOim14gImARNAiNwGuX2ZSaLStaz5GfrWZ81hEvKl36lQuwtE10v1BHPsiERZnYUzFNwmncwCCVH5rR0fFADC2XyGXE3YdOUD2SvY96CNRRS_Fy0LSi2au9nUKY3xszCSeOs6IXAHtRgzei9v3PN4QJGixp_MV8pItv0SvQqD_H9gJ9a53k28aKwY2ls2usEWt7Xxtu3QJVC14bvVTxTfn75QBFL-VquvTQr7RsLGlrgrYCRg-p53_BGCujqi72x8-gHhaKTTqH03Wi9UwIest0XaMoxFzL2-Y5mWcdEc8ohLtV-rmbH7WNUBFPt-xEDXRNGM2_objp0Q_7wmhaMmCt8NxmqaHnfAnQKpIKbRsUnpBgGqUZWk12qV_E_9A_m9pOw" style="color: #1a1a1a; text-decoration: underline;">
            Rise by We
           </a>
           , in New York
          </p>
         </li>
         <li style="margin: 3.75px 0 3.75px 7.5px; mso-special-format: bullet;">
          <p style="color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0;">
           Launched a grade school for young entrepreneurs,
           <a href="https://email.mg2.substack.com/c/eJxFkcvO3CAMhZ9m2GUUbrksWHTT14gcMAkaAhE4HeXtyz9TqRIyiGP7WJ8tEG653ObMldhPWOg-0SR814hEWNhVsSzBGT6ISWo1M2eU45OeWKiLL4gHhGioXMjOa43BAoWcPhV9LzTbDR-dWx0o3w-8507MctXaTmp2XngA__WFywVMFg3-wXLnhCyaneisD_nrIX63QzteZYXkWkbMJ5anzUf7h0LBRqzt-cZ3Lq-uInURrmT37izhgHJ31e45xw42dB0mKngWTK1fgPhPY8GIXvBeipkLPfLxyZ9KisH7dQS7zn7SKAflNCo_zNY7LcVD9ccmnvVaK4F9_QzEikmZ1lxC2pr82uHA-BEanqXdx5UC3QsmWCO6Lzn6LuDDctnaYKUtxi1ADTsfeyEGLZQWX1INrVRympSeWXN2uVWl_6Z_AbnEoWE" style="color: #1a1a1a; text-decoration: underline;">
            WeGrow
           </a>
           , under the leadership of Adam\xe2\x80\x99s wife, Rebekah
          </p>
         </li>
         <li style="margin: 3.75px 0 3.75px 7.5px; mso-special-format: bullet;">
          <p style="color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0;">
           Acquired coding boot camp Flatiron School
          </p>
         </li>
         <li style="margin: 3.75px 0 3.75px 7.5px; mso-special-format: bullet;">
          <p style="color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0;">
           Acquired Meetup for $200 million
          </p>
         </li>
         <li style="margin: 3.75px 0 3.75px 7.5px; mso-special-format: bullet;">
          <p style="color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0;">
           Acquired MissionU, a one-year vocational bootcamp, under the WeGrow brand
          </p>
         </li>
         <li style="margin: 3.75px 0 3.75px 7.5px; mso-special-format: bullet;">
          <p style="color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0;">
           Acquired Teem, a facility management software company, for $100 million
          </p>
         </li>
         <li style="margin: 3.75px 0 3.75px 7.5px; mso-special-format: bullet;">
          <p style="color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0;">
           Raised another $3 billion from SoftBank
          </p>
         </li>
         <li style="margin: 3.75px 0 3.75px 7.5px; mso-special-format: bullet;">
          <p style="color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0;">
           Legally changes its name to The We Company, as part of Neumann\xe2\x80\x99s expanded vision "to encompass all aspects of people's lives, in both physical and digital worlds"
          </p>
         </li>
         <li style="margin: 3.75px 0 3.75px 7.5px; mso-special-format: bullet;">
          <p style="color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0;">
           Updated the company\xe2\x80\x99s mission to \xe2\x80\x9celevate the world\xe2\x80\x99s consciousness.\xe2\x80\x9d
          </p>
         </li>
         <li style="margin: 3.75px 0 3.75px 7.5px; mso-special-format: bullet;">
          <p style="color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0;">
           Nearly sold over half the company to SoftBank for $16 billion before SoftBank pulled out and invested $2 billion at a $47 billion valuation
          </p>
         </li>
         <li style="margin: 3.75px 0 3.75px 7.5px; mso-special-format: bullet;">
          <p style="color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0;">
           Acquired office management platform Managed by Q for $249 million
          </p>
         </li>
         <li style="margin: 3.75px 0 3.75px 7.5px; mso-special-format: bullet;">
          <p style="color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0;">
           Acquired Islands, Prolific, and Waltz in one week
          </p>
         </li>
         <li style="margin: 3.75px 0 3.75px 7.5px; mso-special-format: bullet;">
          <p style="color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0;">
           Acquired workspace management software Space IQ
          </p>
         </li>
         <li style="margin: 3.75px 0 3.75px 7.5px; mso-special-format: bullet;">
          <p style="color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0;">
           Acquired Spacious, which built ground-level drop-in workspaces
          </p>
         </li>
        </ul>
        <p style="color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 1em 0;">
         By the time it filed its
         <a href="https://email.mg2.substack.com/c/eJxFkcGOhCAMhp9mOBoooHDgsJd9DYNQlYyCARzj2y8zc9iE9G_TNn_z4WzFJeXbHKlU8g5jvQ80Ea-yYa2YyVkwj8Eb1oPiUmjijfBMSUVCGeeMuNuwmZpPJMc5bcHZGlL8bFAKkqxmYFppxq30wJ3rgU5sUpJalFx75-nX154-YHRo8IX5ThHJZtZaj_LgPw_4be-6rq6g65b0atVPdmt4YWkp-sXmpt5W24RJziXwllFKGdOcgWQagAqt31ODageBL6xb606CAQqMctBtbGBDxzrBoZ_nabBu0rOSyHvhJYq51272ksND0H2BrpxTqdY9O5d2kk1MdUo5xKW1n6vdcfs0GpSx6X7GUO8Ro5029F9e9Yv9Q3BcMGJu3-FHWxtsNlCAXoKQ8OXTgHLBlRJSk-bsU9uK_6Z_6GiT1Q" style="color: #1a1a1a; text-decoration: underline;">
          S-1
         </a>
         to go public on August 14, 2019, Neumann\xe2\x80\x99s company had transformed from WeWork, a coworking company, to The We Company, which did a little bit of everything. That\xe2\x80\x99s when things started to fall apart.
        </p>
